<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Privacy Policy - PaKoNa</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-b from-pink-50 via-white to-pink-50 text-gray-800">

  <!-- Container -->
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-pink-600">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">Effective Date: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></p>
      <div class="mt-4 border-b border-gray-200"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      At <span class="font-semibold text-pink-600">PaKoNa</span>, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our services.
    </p>

    <!-- Section 1 -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-pink-500 mt-8 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 pl-2 text-gray-700">
      <li>Account information: name, email, password , profile info</li>
      <li>Messages and interactions with other users</li>
      <li>Usage data, such as logins and swipes</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Section 2 -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-pink-500 mt-8 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 pl-2 text-gray-700">
      <li>To provide matching and messaging functionality</li>
      <li>To improve our service and user experience</li>
      <li>To enforce our terms and community guidelines</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Section 3 -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-pink-500 mt-8 mb-3">3. Sharing Your Data</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      We do not sell or rent your data. We may share it with trusted service providers for essential operations (e.g., cloud hosting) or if required by law.
    </p>

    <!-- Section 4 -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-pink-500 mt-8 mb-3">4. Data Security</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      We use encryption, secure databases, and access controls to protect your information. However, no online service can guarantee complete security.
    </p>

    <!-- Section 5 -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-pink-500 mt-8 mb-3">5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      You can request to delete or update your data by contacting our support team at 
      <a href="mailto: pakonaMeet@gmail.com" class="text-pink-600 font-medium hover:underline">pakonaMeet@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>

    <!-- Section 6 -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-pink-500 mt-8 mb-3">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We’ll notify you of significant changes via your dashboard or email.
    </p>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="mt-10 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">
      © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> PaKoNa Meet. All rights reserved.
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
